My Personalized Neovim Configuration

General options and keymaps are done in the init.lua file, and plugin
configuration is done in the lua/settings/ directory.

Plugins are managed with packer. Here is a list of plugins:
 - Project
 - Bufferline
 - Lualine
 - Alpha
 - Telescope
 - CMP
 - Lsp-Zero
 - LuaSnip
 - Treesitter

Directory Structure

├── after
│   └── ftplugin
│       ├── asm.vim
│       ├── assembly.vim
│       ├── html.erb.lua
